2%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20Paris-based%20AI%20company%2C%20Ask%20Mona%2C%20to%20create%20chatbots%20that%20allow%20online%20and%20in-person%20visitors%20to%20have%20conversations%20with%20the%2012%20statues%20in%20its%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScanning%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EQR%20codes%20located%20near%20the%20sculptures%20%E2%80%94%20or%20online%20%E2%80%94%20starts%20an%20audio%20conversation%20with%20a%20chatbot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20garden%20statues%20%26quot%3Bwill%20reveal%20their%20secrets%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20palace%20said%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20Instagram%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDLShtdgp9d4%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20the%20new%20tool%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Singapore%2C%20striking%20up%20conversations%20with%20the%20Apollo%20Fountain%20and%20Neptune's%20Fountain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d37f1241-868b-47f7-bb45-6aeec69049f6%5C%22%3EInformative%20but%20lacking%20personality%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Apollo%20Basin%20is%20brought%20back%20into%20service%2C%20after%20its%20restoration%2C%20in%20the%20gardens%20of%20the%20Palace%20of%20Versailles%20on%20March%2029%2C%202024%20in%20Versailles%20%2C%20France.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685b79d3f748d8c055f44dec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20have%20never%20been%20to%20Versailles%2C%20but%20I%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20chatbot%20pretending%20to%20be%20the%20Apollo%20Fountain.%3Cp%3ELuc%20Castel%2FGetty%20Images)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20tried%20speaking%20with%20the%20Apollo%20Fountain%2C%20a%2015th-century%20golden%20fountain%20by%20French%20sculptor%20Jean-Baptiste%20Tuby.%20The%20chatbot%20immediately%20launched%20into%20an%20elaborate%20description%20of%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fountain%20symbolizes%20the%20dawn%2C%20the%20moment%20when%20light%20spreads%20over%20the%20world.%20It's%20a%20reflection%20of%20power%20and%20renewal%2C%20much%20like%20the%20reign%20of%20the%20Sun%20King%2C%20Louis%20XIV%2C%20who%20saw%20himself%20in%20my%20image%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chatbot%20told%20me%20in%20a%20deep%2C%20somber%20male%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20basic%20questions%20about%20who%20created%20the%20sculpture%20and%20when%20it%20was%20last%20restored%2C%20I%20threw%20some%20curveballs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20you%20tell%20me%20a%20joke%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20much%20as%20I%20enjoy%20bringing%20light%20to%20the%20world%2C%20I%20must%20stay%20true%20to%20my%20role%20here.%20I'm%20a%20symbol%20of%20power%2C%20grace%2C%20and%20eternal%20renewal%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20responded.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20can%20certainly%20brighten%20your%20day%20with%20stories%20of%20art%2C%20history%2C%20and%20myth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20then%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20would%20like%20to%20hear%20more%20about%20the%20symbolism%20of%20the%20fountain.%20I%20did%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20what%20the%20sculpture%20was%20thinking%2C%20it%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20Apollo%2C%20I%20am%20always%20focused%20on%20my%20eternal%20task%3A%20guiding%20the%20sun%20across%20the%20sky.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20my%20luck%20with%20the%2015th-century%20Neptune's%20Fountain.%20I%20asked%20when%20it%20was%20made%20and%20what%20material%20it%20was%20made%20of%2C%20and%20received%20substantial%20answers.%20The%20voice%20was%20the%20same%20male%20voice%20from%20the%20earlier%20sculpture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20what%20details%20first-time%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Evisitors%20should%20look%20out%20for%2C%20the%20chatbot%20suddenly%20went%20silent%2C%20not%20capturing%20my%20voice.%20It%20took%20a%20couple%20of%20website%20refreshes%20to%20get%20it%20to%20answer%20my%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%