%20popular%20real%20estate%20website%20in%20the%20country%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-fights-push-brokerages-real-estate-listings-more-exclusive-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethreatening%20to%20ban%20her%20clients'%20listings%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20its%20search%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20each%20instance%2C%20the%20emails%20said%2C%20Knoll%20had%20marketed%20a%20home%20for%20sale%20without%20quickly%20sharing%20the%20listing%20with%20Zillow.%20Knoll%20tells%20me%20the%20homes%20weren't%20ready%20to%20debut%20on%20the%20search%20portal%2C%20which%20tracks%20price%20cuts%20and%20how%20long%20the%20house%20has%20been%20on%20the%20market%20%E2%80%94%20instead%2C%20she%20and%20her%20clients%20opted%20to%20tease%20them%20on%20the%20Compass%20site%20first%2C%20where%20they%20could%20freely%20test%20prices%20and%20gauge%20interest%20before%20sharing%20more%20widely.%20Those%20decisions%20now%20leave%20Knoll%20on%20thin%20ice%3A%20Starting%20June%2030%2C%20any%20of%20her%20listings%20that%20follow%20a%20similar%20path%20will%20be%20denied%20from%20Zillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20let%20them%20bully%20me%20into%20doing%20things%20that%20are%20detrimental%20to%20my%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20Knoll%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-new-real-estate-agent-listings-rules-homebuyers-search-homes-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewar%20over%20%26quot%3Bhidden%26quot%3B%20home%20listings%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20getting%20ugly.%20At%20the%20core%20of%20the%20dispute%20is%20who%20gets%20to%20see%20houses%20for%20sale%20in%20America%2C%20and%20where%20buyers%20will%20have%20to%20go%20to%20find%20those%20listings.%20The%20bitter%20feud%20features%20two%20of%20the%20real%20estate%20industry's%20true%20behemoths.%20In%20one%20corner%20is%20Compass%2C%20the%20nation's%20largest%20real%20estate%20brokerage%20by%20sales%20volume%2C%20which%20argues%20that%20sellers%20should%20have%20more%20control%20over%20who%20gets%20access%20to%20their%20listings.%20In%20the%20other%20is%20Zillow%2C%20the%20ubiquitous%20home%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-a-zestimate-zillow-home-value-algorithm-history-accuracy-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZestimate%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20essential%20repository%20for%20both%20buyers%20and%20sellers%2C%20which%20counters%20that%20to%20make%20the%20market%20fair%2C%20most%20home%20listings%20should%20be%20available%20as%20widely%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Compass%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompass-zillow-lawsuit-homebuyers-search-listing-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esued%20Zillow%20in%20federal%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20claiming%20the%20company's%20threats%20to%20ban%20certain%20listings%20violated%20antitrust%20laws.%20So%20here%20we%20are%2C%20with%20real%20estate's%20power%20players%20duking%20it%20out%20on%20social%20media%2C%20in%20email%20blasts%2C%20and%20now%20in%20the%20judicial%20system.%20Compass%20and%20Zillow%20may%20be%20the%20faces%20of%20this%20fight%2C%20but%20pretty%20much%20everyone%20in%20the%20industry%20has%20a%20financial%20stake%20in%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20battle%20has%20mostly%20caught%20the%20eye%20of%20real%20estate%20wonks%20who%20live%20and%20breathe%20this%20stuff%2C%20everyday%20consumers%20can't%20afford%20to%20ignore%20it%20any%20longer.%20And%20though%20Zillow%20says%20it's%20trying%20to%20snuff%20out%20hidden%20home%20listings%2C%20its%20policy%20could%20actually%20end%20up%20pushing%20more%20properties%20into%20the%20shadows.%20Buyers%20and%20sellers%20are%20stuck%20in%20the%20middle%20%E2%80%94%20the%20changes%20could%20mean%20they%20risk%20inadvertently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-listings-real-estate-agents-hidden-clear-cooperation-decision-nar-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epassing%20over%20their%20dream%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20listings%20get%20tougher%20to%20find%2C%20or%20they%20may%20wind%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-homebuying-rule-sign-buyer-representation-agreement-realtors-lawsuit-settlement-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etied%20to%20an%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20can%20show%20them%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20market.%20In%20the%20most%20extreme%20cases%2C%20sellers%20may%20find%20that%20their%20home%20has%20been%20blacklisted%20from%20the%20top%20destination%20for%20America's%20house%20hunters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ECompass's%20gregarious%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobert-reffkin-compass-ceo-real-estate-career-rise-job-history-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobert%20Reffkin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20incensed%20much%20of%20the%20industry%20by%20fashioning%20his%20company's%20website%20into%20a%20VIP%20room%20where%20buyers%20can%20get%20a%20first%20look%20at%20homes%20for%20sale%20before%20they%20show%20up%20anywhere%20else%20online.%20Some%20of%20this%20%26quot%3Bexclusive%20inventory%26quot%3B%20is%20advertised%20for%20anyone%20to%20see%20(well%2C%20if%20they%20click%20to%20Compass%20dot-com)%2C%20while%20other%20homes%20are%20even%20more%20secretive%20%E2%80%94%20posted%20in%20an%20internal%20database%20that%20only%20Compass%20agents%20and%20their%20clients%20can%20access.%20I've%20written%20a%20lot%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-association-realtors-rules-commissions-zillow-home-search-pocket-listings-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhy%20Reffkin%20is%20chasing%20this%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20it's%20good%20for%20business.%20In%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025%2C%20almost%20half%20of%20sellers%20represented%20by%20Compass%20agents%20started%20out%20by%20listing%20their%20home%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bprivate%20exclusive%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20company's%20internal%20system.%20Compass%20can%20then%20use%20that%20trove%20of%20exclusive%20listings%20to%20lure%20more%20agents%20and%20clients%20who%20are%20eager%20to%20get%20a%20look%20inside%20that%20private%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZillow%20hates%20all%20this%20%E2%80%94%20listings%20are%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20search%20portals%20like%20Zillow%20want%20them%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20The%20company%20also%20brings%20in%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20its%20revenue%20by%20selling%20leads%3A%20If%20a%20buyer%20signals%20interest%20in%20a%20listing%2C%20Zillow%20will%20typically%20pass%20along%20their%20contact%20information%20to%20an%20agent%20who%20pays%20for%20access%20to%20its%20broad%20user%20base.%20But%20Zillow%20argues%20the%20stakes%20extend%20well%20beyond%20its%20own%20bottom%20line.%20The%20company%20says%20that%20Compass'%20moves%20undermine%20the%20fairness%20and%20transparency%20of%20the%20entire%20housing%20market.%20When%20a%20house%20is%20marketed%20publicly%20to%20buyers%2C%20Zillow%20says%2C%20it%20should%20be%20available%20%3Cem%3Eeverywhere%3C%2Fem%3E.%20By%20holding%20back%20some%20listings%20for%20itself%2C%20the%20theory%20goes%2C%20Compass%20is%20gatekeeping%20for%20its%20own%20gain%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20sellers.%20In%20an%20effort%20to%20fight%20back%2C%20Zillow%20will%20start%20banning%20listings%20that%20run%20afoul%20of%20the%20openness%20mantra%20on%20June%2030.%20If%20you%20don't%20share%20your%20listing%20with%20Zillow%20almost%20as%20soon%20as%20it's%20available%20for%20the%20public%20to%20see%2C%20you%20can't%20share%20it%20with%20Zillow%20later.%20The%20company%20has%20spent%20the%20past%20month%20warning%20agents%20like%20Knoll%20of%20the%20impending%20blockade%20by%20flagging%20listings%20that%20violate%20the%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompass's%20lawsuit%20against%20Zillow%2C%20filed%20a%20week%20before%20enforcement%20of%20that%20ban%20was%20set%20to%20begin%2C%20accuses%20the%20real%20estate%20behemoth%20of%20using%20its%20%26quot%3Bmonopoly%20power%26quot%3B%20to%20force%20people%20to%20advertise%20their%20homes%20on%20its%20website.%20Reffkin%20has%20framed%20it%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20%26quot%3Bchoice%20versus%20control%26quot%3B%3A%20In%20his%20telling%2C%20the%20so-called%20Zillow%20Ban%20isn't%20a%20moralistic%20stand%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20power%20grab.%20Sellers%2C%20he%20says%2C%20should%20be%20able%20to%20advertise%20their%20homes%20wherever%20and%20however%20they%20want%2C%20and%20they%20have%20valid%20reasons%20for%20doing%20so%20off%20Zillow.%20Compass'%20lawsuit%20is%20hardly%20a%20surprise.%20Reffkin%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-fight-clear-cooperation-realtors-zillow-pocket-listings-homes-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epicking%20a%20fight%20over%20home%20listings%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20almost%20a%20year%20at%20this%20point%2C%20and%20he's%20shown%20no%20signs%20of%20backing%20down%20since%20Zillow%20announced%20the%20coming%20ban%20back%20in%20April.%20At%20a%20companywide%20retreat%20in%20early%20June%2C%20Reffkin%20continued%20his%20crusade%20from%20atop%20the%20stage%20at%20a%20convention%20center%20in%20Denver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20out%20at%20the%20crowd%20of%20Compass%20agents%2C%20Reffkin%20outlined%20the%20debate%20in%20clear%20terms%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20simply%20right%20versus%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20forget%2C%20though%2C%20that%20Reffkin's%20original%20target%20wasn't%20Zillow.%20In%20the%20precursor%20to%20the%20current%20fracas%2C%20the%20CEO%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-association-realtors-lawsuit-settlement-housing-market-homebuying-agents-commissions-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eembattled%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20obscure%20rule%20known%20as%20the%20clear%20cooperation%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NAR%20is%20one%20of%20America's%20most%20influential%20trade%20groups.%20It%20oversees%20more%20than%201.5%20million%20members%20and%20effectively%20controls%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20country's%20multiple%20listing%20services%2C%20local%20databases%20where%20details%20on%20homes%20for%20sale%20are%20shared%20widely%20among%20real%20estate%20agents.%20The%20MLSes%20also%20feed%20this%20info%20to%20search%20portals%20like%20Zillow%2C%20which%20then%20compile%20the%20data%20to%20give%20both%20serious%20buyers%20and%20casual%20lurkers%20a%20clear%20view%20of%20the%20market%2C%20free%20of%20charge.%20In%202019%2C%20NAR%20unveiled%20the%20clear%20cooperation%20policy%2C%20which%20required%20agents%20to%20put%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20MLS%20within%20one%20business%20day%20of%20publicly%20marketing%20them.%20A%20sign%20in%20the%20front%20yard%2C%20an%20email%20to%20clients%2C%20or%20a%20Facebook%20post%20would%20all%20trigger%20the%20rule.%20The%20policy%20is%20supposed%20to%20prevent%20firms%20like%20Compass%20from%20advertising%20home%20listings%20on%20their%20own%20websites%20without%20quickly%20sharing%20them%20to%20the%20MLS%20and%20participants%20like%20Zillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EListing%20a%20home%20on%20Zillow%20may%20sound%20like%20a%20no-brainer.%20Just%20show%20your%20house%20to%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%2C%20then%20wait%20for%20the%20offers%20to%20roll%20in.%20Reffkin%2C%20however%2C%20argues%20that%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%20isn't%20best%20for%20sellers.%20The%20MLSes%2C%20and%20by%20extension%2C%20Zillow%2C%20show%20how%20long%20a%20house%20has%20been%20on%20the%20market%20and%20how%20many%20times%20the%20seller%20has%20cut%20the%20price.%20Zillow%20also%20displays%20a%20heap%20of%20information%20that%20sellers%20may%20not%20want%20tied%20to%20their%20listing%3A%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-my-zestimate-accurate-home-prices-obsession-zillow-algorithm-homeowner-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZestimate%20with%20questionable%20accuracy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-buying-check-hidden-financial-risk-climate-crisis-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclimate-risk%20assessment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20highlights%20the%20chances%20of%20flooding%2C%20a%20running%20tab%20of%20all%20the%20times%20a%20deal%20fell%20through.%20That%20kind%20of%20info%2C%20Reffkin%20says%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuyers-sellers-realtor-agent-commissions-saving-rule-changes-lawsuit-settlement-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egives%20buyers%20leverage%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20hurts%20the%20seller%20(others%20in%20the%20industry%20tell%20me%20that%20price%20drops%20can%20signal%20a%20seller%20is%20ready%20to%20make%20a%20deal%2C%20and%20that%20this%20info%20could%20actually%20draw%20more%20attention%20to%20a%20property).%20Compass%20agents%20instead%20advise%20sellers%20to%20adopt%20a%20%26quot%3B3-phased%20marketing%20strategy%26quot%3B%20that%20allows%20them%20to%20test%20the%20waters%20within%20the%20safe%20confines%20of%20the%20brokerage%2C%20then%20display%20it%20on%20the%20Compass%20website%2C%20and%20finally%20share%20it%20widely%20on%20the%20MLS%20and%20everywhere%20else%20(94%25%20of%20Compass%20private%20exclusives%20last%20year%20eventually%20made%20it%20on%20the%20MLS%2C%20Zillow%2C%20and%20everywhere%20else).%20By%20the%20time%20a%20listing%20is%20plastered%20online%2C%20Compass%20says%2C%20the%20seller%20has%20already%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20tinker%20with%20the%20price%20and%20gauge%20its%20reception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20sort%20of%20model%20technically%20violated%20the%20NAR's%20clear%20cooperation%20policy%2C%20though%20enforcement%20was%20spotty%20at%20best.%20Local%20MLSes%20were%20left%20to%20act%20as%20the%20cops%2C%20but%20they%20either%20weren't%20always%20on%20top%20of%20it%20or%20simply%20chose%20to%20ignore%20violations.%20The%20answer%2C%20Reffkin%20argued%20for%20months%2C%20was%20for%20the%20NAR%20to%20simply%20get%20rid%20of%20it%20altogether.%20In%20April%2C%20after%20months%20of%20debate%20and%20speculation%2C%20the%20organization%E2%80%A6punted.%20It%20released%20an%20attempt%20at%20a%20compromise%20that%20satisfied%20nobody%2C%20keeping%20the%20policy%20mostly%20intact%20and%20once%20again%20leaving%20local%20MLSes%20to%20sort%20out%20some%20of%20the%20finer%20details.%20With%20NAR%20dodging%20the%20issue%20and%20home-search%20portals%20still%20facing%20an%20existential%20threat%20from%20the%20growing%20number%20of%20hidden%20listings%2C%20Zillow%20stepped%20in%20as%20the%20judge%2C%20jury%2C%20and%20enforcer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20surprise%20announcement%20in%20early%20April%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20would%20start%20banning%20homes%20that%20didn't%20adhere%20to%20the%20basic%20tenet%20of%20clear%20cooperation%3A%20sharing%20a%20listing%20in%20the%20MLS%20within%20one%20business%20day%20of%20marketing%20it%20to%20the%20public.%20The%20search%20giant%20has%20since%20clarified%20a%20few%20things.%20Agents%20get%20two%20warnings%20before%20getting%20hit%20with%20a%20ban%20on%20their%20third%20non-compliant%20listing.%20Once%20a%20house%20is%20banned%2C%20it's%20on%20the%20blacklist%20as%20long%20as%20the%20seller%20stays%20with%20that%20brokerage%20%E2%80%94%20the%20client%20of%20a%20Compass%20agent%2C%20for%20example%2C%20would%20have%20to%20ditch%20Compass%20entirely%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20get%20back%20in%20Zillow's%20good%20graces.%20And%20even%20agents%20who%20have%20gotten%20hit%20with%20a%20ban%20in%20the%20past%20can%20have%20future%20listings%20appear%20on%20Zillow%2C%20as%20long%20as%20they%20follow%20the%20prescribed%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20ban%20is%20now%20at%20the%20center%20of%20Compass'%20lawsuit%20against%20Zillow.%20Compass'%20filings%20in%20the%20case%20refer%20to%20the%20policy%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20mandate%20that%20only%20a%20monopolist%20would%20adopt%2C%26quot%3B%20sacrificing%20some%20listings%20in%20the%20short%20term%20to%20maintain%20its%20market%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20banned%20a%20seller%20for%20offering%20a%20product%20on%20their%20own%20website%20first.%20That's%20what%20Zillow%20is%20doing%20in%20real%20estate%2C%26quot%3B%20Reffkin%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20Monday%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20lawsuit%20was%20filed.%20%26quot%3BConsumers%20should%20have%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20how%20they%20sell%20their%20homes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Zillow%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20company%20believes%20the%20claims%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20are%20unfounded%20and%20will%20vigorously%20defend%20against%20them.%20According%20to%20Zillow%2C%20the%20listing%20standards%20are%20designed%20to%20%26quot%3Bensure%20transparency%2C%20equal%20opportunity%2C%20and%20broad%20visibility%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20helping%20sellers%20get%20the%20best%20price%20and%20providing%20buyers%20with%20access%20to%20all%20the%20homes%20available%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLimiting%20visibility%20hurts%20buyers%20and%20sellers%2C%20disadvantages%20smaller%20brokerages%2C%20and%20undermines%20an%20open%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20focus%20remains%20on%20creating%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20that%20serves%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20everyone%20in%20the%20homebuying%20and%20selling%20journey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20the%20ban%20doesn't%20do%3A%20Get%20rid%20of%20all%20hidden%20listings.%20The%20semi-public%20homes%20advertised%20only%20on%20a%20single%20site%20may%20be%20blocked%2C%20but%20Zillow's%20policy%2C%20like%20the%20NAR's%20clear%20cooperation%20rule%2C%20allows%20agents%20to%20use%20that%20more%20secretive%20option%20of%20sharing%20a%20home%20with%20other%20agents%20in%20their%20brokerage%20%E2%80%94%20without%20putting%20the%20listing%20in%20the%20MLS%20or%20Zillow.%20The%20walls%20around%20the%20gardens%20may%20change%20somewhat%2C%20but%20they%20are%20still%20intact.%20And%20while%20Compass%20is%20probably%20the%20loudest%20company%20doing%20this%2C%20it's%20far%20from%20the%20only%20one.%20Howard%20Hanna%20has%20%26quot%3BFind%20It%20First.%26quot%3B%20Douglas%20Elliman%20has%20%26quot%3BBlack%20Label%26quot%3B%20private%20listings.%20Corcoran%20has%20%26quot%3BCorcoran%20Reserve.%26quot%3B%20The%2010%20largest%20brokerage%20brands%20handled%20roughly%2060%25%20of%20US%20home%20sales%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20T3%20Sixty%2C%20a%20consulting%20firm%20for%20residential%20real%20estate%20brokerages.%20As%20I've%20written%20before%2C%20if%20even%20a%20few%20big%20companies%20lean%20heavily%20into%20hidden%20listings%2C%20they%20could%20trigger%20a%20domino%20effect%20across%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20even%20thornier%20for%20homes%20marketed%20on%20Compass'%20website%20but%20not%20entered%20into%20the%20MLS.%20Zillow%20is%20unequivocal%20here%2C%20but%20it's%20hard%20to%20argue%20that%20a%20house%20listed%20on%20Compass'%20website%20is%20really%20%3Cem%3Ehidden%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20it%20may%20not%20be%20in%20the%20MLS%20data%20feeds%20or%20Zillow%2C%20but%20anyone%20can%20see%20it%20by%20visiting%20Compass%20dot-com.%20By%20discouraging%20agents%20from%20sharing%20homes%20for%20anyone%20to%20see%2C%20Zillow%20may%20actually%20end%20up%20forcing%20agents%20to%20lean%20more%20heavily%20on%20the%20secret%20%26quot%3Boffice%20exclusives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20unintended%20effect%20of%20that%20is%20actually%20pushing%20these%20listings%20deeper%20and%20deeper%20into%20the%20shadows%2C%20making%20them%20harder%20for%20people%20to%20find%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mike%20DelPrete%2C%20a%20tech%20strategist%20and%20scholar-in-residence%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Colorado%20Boulder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Zillow%20spokesperson%20tells%20me%20they%20believe%20the%20policy%20will%20have%20the%20opposite%20effect.%20And%20while%20it'll%20take%20some%20time%20to%20see%20how%20things%20play%20out%2C%20I%20do%20think%20it's%20safe%20to%20say%20that%20buyers%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20see%20all%20the%20listings%20in%20one%20place.%20Sure%2C%20you%20could%20hop%20around%20the%20websites%20of%20all%20the%20big%20brokerages%20and%20maybe%20piece%20together%20the%20market%20that%20way.%20But%20wouldn't%20it%20be%20nicer%20to%20cruise%20to%20one%20website%20and%20scroll%20through%20everything%20that's%20available%3F%20Glenn%20Kelman%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Redfin%2C%20another%20home-search%20portal%20that%20has%20instituted%20a%20policy%20similar%20to%20Zillow's%2C%20certainly%20thinks%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20shouldn't%20have%20to%20go%20to%2010%20different%20websites%20to%20see%2010%20different%20sets%20of%20inventory%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelman%20told%20me%20back%20in%20April.%20%26quot%3BThat%20will%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20consumers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fantasy%20I%20just%20described%2C%20though%2C%20has%20never%20really%20existed.%20Pocket%20listings%20have%20always%20been%20a%20part%20of%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20buyers%20have%20always%20relied%20on%20agents%20to%20unearth%20the%20homes%20they%20couldn't%20find%20on%20their%20own.%20Hidden%20home%20listings%20aren't%20new.%20But%20we're%20about%20to%20find%20out%20just%20how%20much%20more%20prevalent%20they%20could%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjames-rodriguez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20reporter%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20Discourse%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20