2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I've%20been%20reading%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fsapphirereserve%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Er%2FSapphireReserve%3C%2Fa%3E%20subreddit%20with%20glee%2C%20seeing%20some%20of%20the%20former%20evangelists%20of%20the%20card%20defeated%20by%20its%20new%20fee.%20The%20main%20post%20about%20the%20news%3A%20%26quot%3BWelp.%20It's%20bad%20and%20official.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20should%20note%20here%20that%20the%20card%20may%20indeed%20still%20be%20a%20good%20deal%20for%20some%20people%20%E2%80%94%20it%20matters%20how%20much%20you%20spend%2C%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20rewards%2Fperks%20you're%20most%20interested%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20perks%2C%20however%2C%20are%20not%20exactly%20what%20everyone%20wants%2C%20like%20Apple%20TV%2B%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-music%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%20Music%3C%2Fa%3E%20subscriptions%20(less%20appealing%20for%20a%20Spotify%20user).%20There%20are%20credits%20for%20certain%20hotels%20from%20Chase's%20selection%20of%20hand-picked%20hotels%20(which%20may%20not%20be%20the%20ones%20you%20want).%20If%20you%20spend%20%2475%2C000%20a%20year%20on%20the%20card%2C%20you%20will%20get%20status%20on%20Southwest%20Airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FChaseSapphire%2Fcomments%2F1ldl7vz%2Fcomment%2Fmy9440k%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERedditor%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BWho%20is%20spending%20%2475k%20per%20year%20on%20this%20card%20that%20also%20wants%20status%20on%20Southwest%20Airlines%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Chase%2C%20it%20touts%208X%20points%20on%20all%20Chase%20Travel%20purchases%2C%20which%20is%20up%20from%205X%20on%20flights%2C%20but%20slightly%20down%20from%2010X%20on%20hotels%20and%20car%20rentals.%20It%20also%20touts%204X%20points%20on%20flights%20and%20hotels%20purchased%20directly%20with%20the%20airline%20or%20hote