%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20months%20of%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20Aditya%20pieced%20together%20a%20functioning%20machine.%20The%20KrushiBot%20can%20carry%20a%2016-litre%20tank%2C%20runs%20on%20a%2012V%20rechargeable%20battery%2C%20and%20is%20controlled%20using%20a%20NodeMCU%2C%20a%20Wi-Fi-enabled%20microcontroller%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F443066%2Faadiwasi-janjagruti-tribal-mobile-journalism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econnects%20to%20a%20mobile%20phone%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20the%20phone%2C%20the%20farmer%20can%20move%20the%20robot%20in%20any%20direction%20and%20control%20the%20sprayer.%20The%20NodeMCU%20receives%20the%20signal%20and%20instructs%20the%20motors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-23T083109.408_11zon-1750647689.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20robot%20helps%20farmers%20to%20spray%20pesticides%20in%20the%20field%20in%20half%20the%20time%20by%20sitting%20in%20one%20place%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-23T083109.408_11zon-1750647689.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-23T083109.408_11zon-1750647689-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-23T083109.408_11zon-1750647689-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-23T083109.408_11zon-1750647689-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-23T083109.408_11zon-1750647689-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-453890%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20robot%20helps%20farmers%20to%20spray%20pesticides%20in%20the%20field%20in%20half%20the%20time%20by%20sitting%20in%20one%20place%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20installed%20a%20360-degree%20camera%20on%20the%20bot%2C%20allowing%20farmers%20to%20get%20a%20real-time%20view%20of%20the%20field%20without%20having%20to%20physically%20walk%20through%20it.%20In%20addition%2C%20he%20installed%20a%20simple%20nut-and-bolt%20mechanism%20that%20lets%20the%20sprayer%20be%20raised%20or%20lowered%20depending%20on%20the%20crop%E2%80%99s%20height.%20This%20is%20a%20practical%20solution%20for%20farms%20that%20grow%20a%20variety%20of%20crops%2C%20such%20as%20tall%20grapevines%20and%20shorter%20plants%20like%20mint.%20This%20adaptability%20makes%20the%20device%20customisable%20and%20farmer-friendly%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20tested%20the%20device%20on%20his%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20grape%20farm%20and%20his%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Epudina%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mint)%20fields.%20He%20wanted%20to%20see%20if%20his%20creation%20could%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20real%20farming%20conditions.%20Both%20trials%20were%20a%20success%2C%20proving%20that%20the%20bot%20is%20a%20low-cost%2C%20practical%20and%20efficient%20working%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20bot%20helps%20different%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20this%2C%20it%20used%20to%20take%20me%20over%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20to%20spray%20the%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sande